profile: Christian Berishaj, better known by his stage name JMSN (pronounced Jameson), is an American singer-songwriter, multi-instrumentalist, record producer, music engineer, and mixer from Detroit, Michigan. His debut album, Priscilla was released in 2012. He wrote and produced the album by himself and also directed the videos accompanying the release.
